{
  "stem": "769.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So by the third day, the teacher, I still seeing her with eye-- they've got the bench there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're not single like here, in the school-- sit, you know, a chair, let me tell you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's a-- the whole-- the long one would sit 10 or there are 8 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you know, it's like you see in the-- in the shul, so like that one, with a table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they're not separate sitting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they pushed me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They told me to go home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They will call me when [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some kids from the farm come in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And while there, it's Christians and Catholics, they got the number one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So it's a quarter, like to say, not officially, not legal-- and it's legal because every province did it at its own way.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I was pushed out from the school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was either eight or nine years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or 10, something like that. 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life from the beginning, you know, when I was in school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the beginning, I started the cheder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the cheder, they just learned us religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was another school that belonged to the Mizrahi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Their got-- they learned there, and they learn like the-- how to do something like arithmetic in Polish, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I-- when I-- when they took me out, my parents took me out from the school, my-- I just learned the basic things-- arithmetic, you know, and spelling.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But not that other things what we needed in life, like science and physics.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, you not need it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What a Jew needed, when he is growing up?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to have children, to have a family, and to make business, and to know 2 times 2 is 4.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's 60, 70, 80 years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
